casebody.data:
Thursday, April 25, 1996

RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-2279. Feichtner v. Ohio Dept. of Transp.

Franklin County, No. 95API01-47. Reported at 75 Ohio St.3d 1411, 661 N.E.2d 759. On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted; sua sponte, discretionary appeal allowed and merit briefing to proceed.

Moyer, C.J., and Resnick, J., dissent. Stratton, J., not participating.
